Name: Average time from Declaration SUBMITTED by EMPLOYEE to Declaration REJECTED by SUPERVISOR
Metric: The average of the duration between activity 'Declaration SUBMITTED by EMPLOYEE' and activity 'Declaration REJECTED by SUPERVISOR'

Name: Average time between Declaration REJECTED by SUPERVISOR and Request Payment
Metric: The average of the duration between activity 'Declaration REJECTED by SUPERVISOR' and activity 'Request Payment'

Name: Average resolution time for cases involving Declaration REJECTED by SUPERVISOR
Metric: The average of the duration between activity 'Declaration REJECTED by SUPERVISOR' and the end of case where activity 'case closure occurs

Name: Total time spent in activities before Declaration REJECTED by SUPERVISOR across all cases
Metric: The sum of the duration between the start of the case and activity 'Declaration REJECTED by SUPERVISOR'

Name: Total time spent in activities after Declaration REJECTED by SUPERVISOR until case closure
Metric: The sum of the duration between activity 'Declaration REJECTED by SUPERVISOR' and the end of case where activity 'case closure occurs

Name: Minimum time from Declaration APPROVED by ADMINISTRATION to Declaration REJECTED by SUPERVISOR
Metric: The minimum of the duration between activity 'Declaration APPROVED by ADMINISTRATION' and activity 'Declaration REJECTED by SUPERVISOR'

Name: Average time from Declaration REJECTED by SUPERVISOR to Declaration SUBMITTED by EMPLOYEE in cases of re-submission
Metric: The average of the duration between activity 'Declaration REJECTED by SUPERVISOR' and activity 'Declaration SUBMITTED by EMPLOYEE'

Name: Total resolution time of cases with Declaration REJECTED by SUPERVISOR leading to case closure without Payment Handled
Metric: The average of the duration between activity 'Declaration REJECTED by SUPERVISOR' and the end of case where activity 'Payment Handled does not occur

Name: Average time from Declaration REJECTED by SUPERVISOR to Declaration APPROVED by PRE_APPROVER in subsequent process steps
Metric: The average of the duration between activity 'Declaration REJECTED by SUPERVISOR' and activity 'Declaration APPROVED by PRE_APPROVER'

Name: Total time from Declaration REJECTED by SUPERVISOR to the next Declaration APPROVED by ADMINISTRATION
Metric: The sum of the duration between activity 'Declaration REJECTED by SUPERVISOR' and activity 'Declaration APPROVED by ADMINISTRATION'

Name: Average time for cases to be resolved after Declaration REJECTED by SUPERVISOR
Metric: comparing those that are eventually approved versus those that are not
Value: The average of the duration between activity 'Declaration REJECTED by SUPERVISOR' and the end of case where activity 'case closure occurs

Name: Minimum time from Declaration REJECTED by SUPERVISOR to any subsequent Declaration REJECTED by PRE_APPROVER
Metric: focusing on process improvement to reduce rejections
Value: The minimum of the duration between activity 'Declaration REJECTED by SUPERVISOR' and activity 'Declaration REJECTED by PRE_APPROVER'

Name: Average time it takes for a Declaration REJECTED by SUPERVISOR to be followed by a Declaration FINAL_APPROVED by SUPERVISOR in revised submissions
Metric: The average of the duration between activity 'Declaration REJECTED by SUPERVISOR' and activity 'Declaration FINAL_APPROVED by SUPERVISOR'

Name: Total time for all activities to occur between Declaration REJECTED by SUPERVISOR and Declaration FINAL_APPROVED by SUPERVISOR in cases of successful resubmission
Metric: The sum of the duration between activity 'Declaration REJECTED by SUPERVISOR' and activity 'Declaration FINAL_APPROVED by SUPERVISOR'
